  "title": "Survey  of Masakwa  Sorghum   Growing Areas in Northeastern Nigeria",
  "abstract": "Masakwa sorghum is a post-rainy season sorghum grown mainly in the Chad Basin area of Borno State, NE Nigeria. Production practices, and the major constraints to production, were assessed in a survey of 24 villages.",
